114
00:17:14,340 --> 00:17:18,670
Apa kau baik-baik saja?

115
00:17:18,670 --> 00:17:21,420
Apa yang tiba-tiba
kau katakan?

116
00:17:23,100 --> 00:17:26,690
Apa kau merasa kesakitan?

117
00:17:27,520 --> 00:17:30,300
Apa itu berarti bahwa kau
berharap aku terluka?

118
00:17:31,570 --> 00:17:34,610
Sayang sekali, aku
merasa sangat sehat,

119
00:17:34,610 --> 00:17:37,290
